<br>
I still can't believe they upped clerics &quot;ability to solo&quot;.  What cleric wants to solo?  Plus if they need to solo they have a few nukes, which I think would be potent enough to solo alone, even if they are not mana efficient.  <br>
<br>
The one thing that I can't stand is VI's silence on the matter.  They haven't done anything to make the complaints stop, of course we've all heard about their great customer service.<br>
<br>
I could be wrong and my perception could be different than someone elses, especially an SK or Pally.  But I urge them to make a warrior and level him (no twinkage) and see how hard it really is.  You can't root a mob to save your as$, nor can you snare.  All you can do is fight and take damage.  That is all we do.  The only thing we do.  Now can you see how it bothers a warrior when another classes AC and HP are very close to his?<br>
<br>
Most of our disciplines are a joke, with the exception of defensive.  Not that the rest suck, but I'm sure the raid leader won't be happy with you when the MT dies and you're MT.  &quot;Sorry defensive doesn't refresh for another 20 minutes&quot;.  There should be a seperate time for offensive and defensive disc. in my opinion.  Even if it doesn't do much for our DPS, it would still just be fun.  That's the point of playing this game isn't?  <br>
<br>
<br>
...just the thoughts from my head...<br>
<br>
