<br>
As far as solo?  A monk will solo more effectively.<br>
<br>
I don't think warriors need a better taunt ablity.  That pretty much trivializes aggro control, which is something that I enjoy having to work with on a raid.  Y'know, that strategy thing.<br>
<br>
I do think maybe they should recieve innate avoidance or absorbtion for damage.  I think Pallies and SK's need that too though, maybe a watered down version.<br>
<br>
