<br>
So, in a nutshell... an SK is a second rate tank, a fifth rate damage dealer, but can draw aggro on command.<br>
<br>
Erm, and disciplines, I won't even go into the joke that are the SK discs. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
